[x] the user should be able to create a new account.
[x] the user should be able to login
[x] the user should be able to view the movies page
[x] the user should be able to add a movie to the favourite page
[x] the user should be able to logout

An ordinary user can only access get requests

[x] The user should not have access to routes that are protected unless logged in.
[x] The user should be directed to the loggin page if not authenticated and trying to access a protected route
[x] The user should be directed to the previous route path on loggin

Admin user
[] The user should be able to edit/delete a movie
[] The user should be able to add new movies

An admin user is capable of performing all requests. (CRUD);